### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@employeeId = 1
@startDate = 2025-01-01
@endDate = 2025-01-31

### Check In
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendances/checkin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": {{employeeId}},
  "date": "2025-01-09T08:00:00.000Z",
  "time": "2025-01-09T08:00:00.000Z"
}

### Check Out
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendances/checkout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": {{employeeId}},
  "date": "2025-01-09T17:00:00.000Z",
  "time": "2025-01-09T17:00:00.000Z"
}

### Check In - Different Day
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendances/checkin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": {{employeeId}},
  "date": "2025-01-08T08:30:00.000Z",
  "time": "2025-01-08T08:30:00.000Z"
