### Get Attendance Summary (Default: Current Month)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances/summary?employeeId={{employeeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Attendance Summary with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances/summary?employeeId={{employeeId}}&startDate={{startDate}}&endDate={{endDate}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Attendance Summary - Different Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances/summary?employeeId=2&startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-01-31
Content-Type: application/json

### Get All Attendances (For Admin HRD)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances/all
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Attendances by Specific Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/attendances/employee/{{employeeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Test Multiple Check-ins Same Day (Edge Case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attendances/checkin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": {{employeeId}},
  "date": "2025-01-07",
  "time": "2025-01-07T09:00:00.000Z"
}

